---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | MPLS LLC" description="MPLS LLC terms of service for our products and services.">
	<section class="bg-brand-900 py-16">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-300 mb-2">Legal</p>
			<h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl">Terms of Service</h1>
			<p class="mt-3 text-brand-200">Last Updated: February 7, 2026</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">1. The Agreement</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">By accessing our website or services, you acknowledge that you are entering a space dedicated to respect, safety, and progressive action. We prioritize the safety of our community above all else.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">2. Age Requirement</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">You must be at least 16 years old to create an account or use Sojorn. We enforce this through an age gate at login. By using our services, you represent that you meet this age requirement.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">3. Zero Tolerance Policy</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">We do not tolerate intolerance. Hate speech, racism, sexism, homophobia, transphobia, ableism, and fascist ideologies are strictly prohibited. Violations may result in content removal, temporary suspension, or permanent bans depending on severity.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">4. No Misinformation</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">We reject the spread of verifiable falsehoods, conspiracy theories, and disinformation campaigns. Posting content designed to deceive or manipulate will result in account termination.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">5. Moderation &amp; Appeals</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">Content is moderated using a combination of automated systems and human review. If your content is removed or your account is actioned, you will be notified and may submit an appeal through the app. Appeals are reviewed individually and decisions are communicated back to you. We are committed to fair and transparent enforcement.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">6. Content Ownership</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">You own the content you create. You grant us a license to display it within the private Sojorn network, but we claim no ownership over your intellectual property and will never sell it to third parties.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">7. Data Usage &amp; Advertising</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">We may use anonymized, non-identifying data to improve platform features, personalize your content feed, and serve privacy-preserving advertisements. We will never use tracking pixels, browser fingerprinting, or cross-app surveillance. Ads are matched to content context and anonymous cohort preferences — never to your personal identity. See our <a href="/privacy" class="text-brand-700 hover:text-brand-800 font-medium transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">8. Liability</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">MPLS LLC provides this service "as is." We are not liable for interactions that occur between users, though we commit to active moderation to maintain community safety.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">9. Governing Law</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">These terms are governed by the laws of the United States and the State of Minnesota. If you are located in the European Union, you also retain any rights granted to you under applicable EU data protection laws, including the GDPR.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">10. Service Modifications</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">We reserve the right to modify or discontinue our services at any time, with or without notice. We will provide reasonable advance notice for significant changes that affect your use of the service.</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
					<p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
						For questions about these terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@mp.ls" class="text-brand-700 hover:text-brand-800 font-medium transition-colors">admin@mp.ls</a>.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
